document_name: Support to MDGs Programming Project Document

outputs.output_descr: The overall goal of the unit will be to support the Government's efforts in achieving the MDGs, through the provision of advice and formulation of new programmes to support government partners, provision of supprt to transition to National Execution of UNDP Projects, communications and advocacy activities to promote UNDP and SIG Partnership, south-south cooperation, and the MDGs, to improve monitoring and oversight of the UNDP Programme Portfolio.

project_descr: Support to UNDP Programming for the Achievement of MDGs
project_title: Support to Programming for Achievement of MDGs
